Pascal Okechukwu aka Cubana Chief Priest has been arrested. He had been invited by the Inspector-General of Police Monitoring Unit in Lagos. On arrival at the Force Headquarters Annex, Lagos, Okechukwu was detained. The popular socialite is the Executive Director of the Cubana group and owner of the Cubana Club. Okechukwu, known for his lavish lifestyle, has a huge following on social media. He is accused of misuse of police escorts and weapons. It was also gathered that he was grilled about his wealth.